description: Partial demolition, alterations and extension in association with the use of the building for commercial, community and residential use (commercial and community purposes to be determined - falling within use classes A1 (shops), A3 (restaurants and cafes), A4 (drinking establishments), B1 (business), D1 (community uses), D2 (leisure and theatre.  Creation of 223 residential flats (118  x 1 bed, 99 x 2 bed, 4 x 3 bed, 2 x 4 bed) including the erection of a three storey building fronting Thorparch Road comprising 5 self contained flats, together with associated access, servicing,  car parking (131 spaces) and landscape works.
